title: Love Live! Nijigasaki High School Idol Club 7th Live! NEW TOKIMEKI LAND
overview: Love Live! Nijigasaki High School Idol Club 7th Live! NEW TOKIMEKI LAND (ラブライブ！虹ヶ咲学園スクールアイドル同好会 7th Live! NEW TOKIMEKI LAND) is Nijigasaki High School Idol Club's seventh solo live concert that will take place at K-Arena Yokohama on October 19 & 20, 2024.
